'''Dia di Tera''' ta un evento anual rond mundo riba dia [[22 di aprel|12 di april]] pa mustra sosten na proteccion di [[medio ambiente]].<ref>[https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/earth-day-2020-climate-change-environment-bees-a8314891.html  Earth Day 2020: What is it and how do people mark it around the world?], Independent.co.uk (21 di april 2020)</ref><ref>[https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/50th-anniversary-earth-day-unites-153700569.html The 50th Anniversary Of Earth Day Unites Tens Of Millions Of People Across The World In Action And A Multi-Platform Event], Yahoo.com (24 di april 2020)</ref>  

Riba e prome Dia di Tera na aña [[1970]] miyones di [[Estadonan Uni di Merka|Mericano]] a mobilisa pa protesta p’e ignorancia ambiental y pa exigi pa tuma un rumbo nobo pa proteha e [[Tera|planeta tera]]. Esaki a conduci na e aprobacion di leynan ambiental emblematica na Merka, incluyendo leynan di aire limpi, awa limpi y especienan den peliger di extincion. Hopi pais a adopta leynan similar. Na 2016 [[Nacionan Uni]] a scoge Dia di Tera como fecha pa firma e [[Acuerdo di Paris]] relaciona cu e crisis di [[cambio di clima]].  

